PrecisRe-appointment of THÉRÈSE PAQUET-SÉVIGNY, of Montreal, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the International Centre for Human Rights and Democratic Development to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective January 31, 1998.
